  <summary date="2023-08-08T22:55:08Z" status="Introduced in House">Student Loan Borrower Relief Act

 This bill revises income-driven repayment plans for federal student loans, including by reducing from 25 years to 15 years the maximum repayment period under these plans. Additionally, the bill makes changes to the Public Service Loan Forgiveness program, including by cancelling a portion of a borrower's student loans after every 12 months of eligible public service employment.</summary>
